{"tid":2440083,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"個新同事比老闆拍兩下肩講咗句「睇好你啦」就好似打咗針咁，成個人痴咗線","createTime":"2021-03-09T16:48:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T16:57:29.000Z","uid":35348,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"494f6e6812a5f763a04035d65a791d54403bd35c","tid":2440083,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T16:48:06.000Z","msg":"上星期做完個細PROJECT，今個星期預咗HEA住做，咁老闆返嚟都照慣例過嚟講兩句，做下PEP TALK，之後就準備HEA<br />\n<br />\n老闆見個新同事第一舍PROJECT，咪過去問下佢做得慣唔慣，有冇乜問題，又話有乜問題隨時同佢講之類之類，最後咪拍一拍肩頭，同佢講「睇好你啦」咪返自己房。<br />\n<br />\n返開工都知呢啲嘢都只係吹下水，呃下班打工仔，唔可信嘅，但係個新同事唔知話佢冇經驗家太單純好，佢信晒老闆講啲嘢，以為老闆真係打算比佢發圍之類之類，係咁CHUR我哋，CHUR埋佢上司即係我阿頭，話要諗下點做點做，又推咗幾個PROJECT出嚟，唔夠十分鐘又問人點睇有乜意見咁&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n個新同事新入職冇幾耐，仲好似係第一份工，我都了解佢對「返工」仲有期望係好究，但係都要認清現實，到底我提唔提佢好？提佢好似又打爆咗佢個希望&hellip;"},{"pid":"364d71ab2674adbffbad876d57f5c553f3429d4f","tid":2440083,"uid":38189,"like":13,"dislike":4,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T16:49:47.000Z","msg":"有上進心好正常 樓主自己懶就唔好阻人發圍啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcecf17d1259505c5e559d071d282d04142854ab","tid":2440083,"uid":15886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T16:49:56.000Z","msg":"講夠針未"},{"pid":"a7fab974154a04953dbc29edc7056653b59a20f4","tid":2440083,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T16:50:06.000Z","msg":"你又講乜撚針呀"},{"pid":"e806d784b596edb8e44223bdc79ecec18f0a22e9","tid":2440083,"uid":72497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T16:50:57.000Z","msg":"呢句說話，同「下次飲茶」意思一 L 樣。<br />\n<br />\n你個新仔真係好可愛<br />\n<br />\n嗱！<br />\n你就係因為咁 HEA 做，就變成咗佢口中阻住佢上位嘅老屎忽啦<br />\n<br />\n跌吉成日有呢啲傑青開 post ，話比老屎忽阻住<br />\n<br />\n你實唔認架，不過佢覺得係囉"},{"pid":"f5828e75b497f42da45de0ba41617d65249cc9e0","tid":2440083,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7fab974154a04953dbc29edc7056653b59a20f4","tid":2440083,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T16:50:06.000Z","msg":"你又講乜撚針呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T16:50:59.000Z","msg":"唉 咁惡做乜"},{"pid":"bdba3e90014e8daa3693a10c1e07225611d92673","tid":2440083,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"364d71ab2674adbffbad876d57f5c553f3429d4f","tid":2440083,"uid":38189,"like":13,"dislike":4,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T16:49:47.000Z","msg":"有上進心好正常 樓主自己懶就唔好阻人發圍啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T16:51:17.000Z","msg":"樓主懶到閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n次次黃昏街站唔見人"},{"pid":"c4f806683c899a5fb5dc685437ea23154045be54","tid":2440083,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdba3e90014e8daa3693a10c1e07225611d92673","tid":2440083,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"364d71ab2674adbffbad876d57f5c553f3429d4f","tid":2440083,"uid":38189,"like":13,"dislike":4,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T16:49:47.000Z","msg":"有上進心好正常 樓主自己懶就唔好阻人發圍啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T16:51:17.000Z","msg":"樓主懶到閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n次次黃昏街站唔見人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T16:52:15.000Z","msg":"未醒"},{"pid":"359097286ba84e7e7865b83eae35abbe5ea53114","tid":2440083,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdba3e90014e8daa3693a10c1e07225611d92673","tid":2440083,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"364d71ab2674adbffbad876d57f5c553f3429d4f","tid":2440083,"uid":38189,"like":13,"dislike":4,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T16:49:47.000Z","msg":"有上進心好正常 樓主自己懶就唔好阻人發圍啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T16:51:17.000Z","msg":"樓主懶到閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n次次黃昏街站唔見人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T16:52:16.000Z","msg":